.. code:: console

   $ exp509 --help
   usage: exp509 [-h] -t N [-T] HOST[:PORT] [HOST[:PORT] ...]

   positional arguments:
     HOST[:PORT]

   options:
     -h, --help         show this help message and exit
     -t, --threshold N  alert when cert expires in N days (or less)
     -T, --TAP          use TAP output

   $ exp509 -t 90 jwilk.net
   jwilk.net: certificate expires on 2021-11-15 05:02

